    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Relocate logs and metrics tabs from the services page. <a href=\"/w/new-logs-metrics-access-buttons\" target=\"_self\">See release update notes</a>.</li>\n<li>Change ownership of Liferay during initContainer</li>\n<li>Enable log rotation in nginx</li>\n<li>Remove Backup UI Compatibility for GCS</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Weekly Autoscale Report emails are sent to projects with zero autoscale activity during the week</li>\n</ul>"
      },
